 spew so much shit you put that Shit monster in Domga to shame dude... <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#242422><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/uterok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Terok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 76<br> <font color=#939393>(8/19/01 10:05:11 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://www.tir.com/~jtcable/blacksquare.gif WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Putting the N into Novel</span><hr size=1> Haha, Chise man you just sucked like 15 paragraphs outta that guy.  <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#000000><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub28.ezboard.com/usynide3.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Synide3</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 457<br> <font color=#939393>(8/19/01 10:37:12 pm)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> <img src="http://www.ezboard.com/images/posticons/pi_sunglasses.gif" align=absmiddle>  Re: Putting the N into Novel</span><hr size=1> Oh man, how can you argue against a post that says ABSOLUTELY FUCKING NOTHING.  Wow, Balrak you never cease to amaze me with your sheer stupidity.  Even though you think you're probably the most intelligent person here, I bet many people would beg to differ.  You sir, are a fucking retard.  I've never seen someone spew out such worthless non-sense with 1 long post.  Purely amazing, I read it all, thx for wasting 7 minutes of my life. <p>omg
